### **4. 29_LiveChartGrid**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes live numeric input streams in a grid-style chart for multiple data points.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveChartGrid - Realtime Data Stream Plotter

LiveChartGrid allows multi-source numeric feeds to be displayed live in scrollable, dynamic charts.

## Features
- Realtime scrolling charts  
- Adjustable refresh speed  
- Matplotlib-based  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/29_LiveChartGrid.git
cd 29_LiveChartGrid
python visualize.py
